snippet.title: Super Farming Boy - Official Trailer | Latin American Games Showcase
snippet.description: Super Farming Boy is an action farming puzzle simulation game developed by LemonChili Soft. With the farm under attack, players must fly, harvest, grow crops & whack enemies with their shape-shifting one-button superpowers. Seek revenge from your evil nemesis, Korpo, who has captured your mom & friends. Super Farming Boy is coming to PC (Steam).
